sequenceDiagram
    participant App as Microservice
    participant Agent as OTEL Agent
    participant Collector as OTEL Collector
    participant Firehose as Kinesis Firehose
    participant XRay as AWS X-Ray
    participant OS as OpenSearch
    participant CW as CloudWatch

    App->>Agent: Send telemetry (traces, logs, metrics)
    Agent->>Collector: Batch & forward
    
    par Trace Processing
        Collector->>XRay: Send traces
        XRay-->>CW: Trace metrics
    and Log Processing
        Collector->>Firehose: Send logs
        Firehose->>OS: Index logs
    end
    
    OS-->>CW: Cluster metrics
    CW->>CW: Trigger alarms if needed
